<h3>My Dashboard</h3>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <div class="body-subdued-block" style="border-radius:10px">
      <p style="text-align:center;"><%= image_tag('reading.png', :style => "opacity:0.2") -%></p>
      <h4 style="text-align:center;margin-top:20px;">Reading Projects</h4>
      <p class="sub-title">These are reading projects that I have been invited to read.</p>
      <p class="centered"><%= link_to "Go to my READING Projects", reading_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-success" -%></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <div class="body-subdued-block" style="border-radius:10px;">
      <p style="text-align:center;"><%= image_tag('writing.png', :style => "opacity:0.2") -%></p>
      <h4 style="text-align:center;margin-top:20px;">Writing Projects</h4>
      <p class="sub-title">These are my writing projects that are in progress.</p>
      <p class="centered"><%= link_to "Go to my WRITING Projects", writing_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-success" -%></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span3">
    <p class="lead" style="border-bottom:2px solid #bbb;">Reading or Writing?</p>
    <p>Whether you like to read or like to write.  There is something for everyone.</p>
    <p>Volunteer to read literary works from a variety of writers. Select the genres you like and are suited for.</p>
    <p>Upload your writing and invite known or random readers to provide you feedback.</p>
  </div>
</div>
